DSpace REST Contract
This repository documents the current DSpace REST API Contract beginning with DSpace version 7.0.
The code that implements this contract is on the main branch of the DSpace backend.
One example client which utilizes this contract is the DSpace frontend DSpace User Interface, built with Angular.io.
